</div>

<!-- SECTION 3: The Damage -->
<div class="blue-white gutter" name="the-damage">
    <div class="container">
        <div class="row">
            <div class="col">
                <a id="the-damage" class="anchor"></a>
                <h2 class="text-center spacer">Your Home is at Risk!</h2>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="row risk-factor align-items-center">
            <div class="col-lg-2 offset-lg-2 col-md-2 offset-md-2 col-sm-3 col-12 text-center">
                <img class="img-fluid risk-img" src="./images/icons/water.png" alt="Water Damage" />
            </div>
            <div class="col-lg-6 col-md-6 col-sm-9 col-12">
                <p>An 1/8" hole in a pipe can leak over 40 litres of water per hour!</p>
                <p class="text-right"><em>&mdash;Angie's List</em></p>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="row risk-factor align-items-center">
            <div class="col-lg-6 offset-lg-2 col-md-6 offset-md-2 col-sm-9 col-12">
                <p>The average claim for water damage from frozen pipes is about $15,000.</p>
                <p class="text-right"><em>&mdash;State Farm Insurance</em></p>
            </div>
            <div class="col-lg-2 col-md-2 col-sm-3 col-12 text-center order-sm-last order-first">
                <img class="img-fluid risk-img" src="./images/icons/temperature.png" alt="High Temperature" />
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="row risk-factor align-items-center">
            <div class="col-lg-2 offset-lg-2 col-md-2 offset-md-2 col-sm-3 col-12 text-center">
                <img class="img-fluid risk-img" src="./images/icons/plug.png" alt="No Power" />
            </div>
            <div class="col-lg-6 col-md-6 col-sm-9 col-12">
                <p>Food in your fridge will begin to spoil as quickly as 4 hours into a power outage.</p>
                <p class="text-right"><em>&mdash;Food and Drug Administration</em></p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

<!-- SECTION 3: Risk Assessment -->
<div class="green-white gutter" name="risk-assessment">
    <div class="container">
        <div class="row">
            <div class="col-xl-5 col-lg-5 offset-lg-1 col-md-8 offset-md-2 col-12">
                <a id="risk-assessment" class="anchor"></a>
                <h2 class="text-center spacer">Assess Your Risk</h2>
                <p>How safe do you think your home away from home&mdash;and you&mdash;are from costly water damage? There are many factors that could raise the cost of your insurance after damage, such as:</p>
                <ul>
                    <li>Number of properties</li>
                    <li>Amount of time spent away</li>
                    <li>Where your property is built</li>
                </ul>
                <p>See how at risk you are by filling out our quick survey!</p>
            </div>
            <div id="assessment" class="col-xl-5 col-lg-5 offset-lg-0 col-md-8 offset-md-2 col-12">
                <form class="assessment-form">
                    <div class="col-12">
                        <label class="mr-sm-2" for="inlineFormCustomSelect">How many properties do you own?</label>
                        <select class="custom-select mr-sm-2" id="inlineFormCustomSelect">
                            <option selected>Choose...</option>
                            <option value="1">One</option>
                            <option value="2">Two to five</option>
                            <option value="3">More than five</option>
                        </select>
                    </div>
                    <br />
                    <div class="col-12">
                        <label class="mr-sm-2" for="inlineFormCustomSelect">How long do you typically leave your properties unoccupied?</label>
                        <select class="custom-select mr-sm-2" id="inlineFormCustomSelect">
                            <option selected>Choose...</option>
                            <option value="1">Never</option>
                            <option value="2">Less than one month at a time</option>
                            <option value="3">2-6 months at a time</option>
                            <option value="4">Over 6 months at a time</option>
                        </select>
                    </div>
                    <br />
                    <div class="col-12">
                        <label class="mr-sm-2">Have you ever had an incident involving water damage occur at your property?</label>
                    </div>
                    <div class="row">
                        <div class="offset-1 col-5">
                            <div class="form-check form-check-inline">
                                <input class="form-check-input" type="radio" name="previousdamage" id="rdoYes" value="Yes">
                                <label class="form-check-label" for="rdoYes">Yes</label>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="col-5">
                            <div class="col-6 form-check form-check-inline">
                                <input class="form-check-input" type="radio" name="previousdamage" id="rdoNo" value="No">
                                <label class="form-check-label" for="rdoNo">No</label>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <br />
                    <div class="col-12">
                        <label class="mr-sm-2">Do you currently own insurance that covers incidents involving water damage?</label>
                    </div>
                    <div class="row">
                        <div class="offset-1 col-5">
                            <div class="form-check form-check-inline">
                                <input class="form-check-input" type="radio" name="insurance" id="rdoInsYes" value="Yes">
                                <label class="form-check-label" for="rdoInsYes">Yes</label>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="col-5">
                            <div class="col-6 form-check form-check-inline">
                                <input class="form-check-input" type="radio" name="insurance" id="rdoInsNo" value="No">
                                <label class="form-check-label" for="rdoInsNo">No</label>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <br />
                    <button type="submit" class="btn btn-block btn-risk-submit">Submit</button>
                </form>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

<!-- SECTION 4: Who Are We -->
<div class="blue-white gutter" name="who-are-we">
    <div class="container">
        <div class="row">
            <div class="col-xl-7 col-lg-6 col-12">
                <table style="height: 100%; width: 100%;">
                    <tbody>
                        <tr>
                            <td>
                                <img class="img-fluid" src="./images/elliott-temp.jpg" />
                            </td>
                        </tr>
                    </tbody>
                </table>
            </div>
            <div class="col-xl-5 col-lg-6 col-12">
                <table style="height: 100%; width: 100%;">
                    <tbody>
                        <tr>
                            <td>
                                <a id="who-are-we" class="anchor"></a>
                                <h2 class="text-center spacer">Who Are We?</h2>
                                <p>syndii&trade; was built by Elliott, cottage owner and engineer, who worried about unseen environmental disasters when he was away from his property, with no easy, reliable solution to solve it.</p>
                                <p>He had friends and family that felt the same way, so he set out to do something about it, something any home owner could easily do.</p>
                                <p>Do you wish to learn more, or just stay in the loop? Sign up for our mailing list!</p>

                                <form asp-action="../Subscribers/Subscribe" class="sign-up">
                                    <div asp-validation-summary="ModelOnly" class="text-danger"></div>
                                    <div class="input-group mb-3">
                                        <input asp-for="Email" type="text" id="emailValidate" placeholder="Enter your email" class="form-control" required>
                                        <span asp-validation-for="Email" class="text-danger"></span>
                                        <div class="input-group-append">
                                            <input class="btn btn-sign-up" value="Submit" type="submit" />
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                    <div class="form-check">
                                        <input asp-for="TermsAndConditions" type="checkbox" class="form-check-input" id="opt-in" required />
                                        <label class="form-check-label" for="opt-in"><small>I have read the <a href="@Url.Action("Terms", "Home")" target="_blank">terms of use</a> and <a href="@Url.Action("Privacy", "Home")" target="_blank">privacy policy</a> and would like to subscribe to the syndii&trade; mailing list</small></label>
                                    </div>
                                </form>
                            </td>
                        </tr>
                    </tbody>
                </table>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

